tweet_raw: Sei v2: Parallelizing the Ethereum Execution EnvironmentSei v2 is poised to become the first parallelized EVM blockchain. This major proposed update from Sei Labs aims to deploy a backward compatible Ethereum execution environment integrated into Sei’s core binary inheriting Sei’s advanced twin turbo consensus mechanism and optimistic parallelization capabilities while remaining fully composable with Sei’s existing wasm environment.This approach means that any Ethereum or Ethereum Layer 2 application can now deploy on Sei to harness Seis speed and throughput and users can interact with Sei using familiar tools such as Metamask. The upgrade is code complete and ready for audit read more here: blog.sei.io/sei-v2-the-first…Developers developers developers:Today Sei allows for Cosmwasm smart contracts which are written in Rust. As Sei continues to garner more developer interest the biggest request has been additional flexibility in the execution environments that Sei supports. Sei Labs has risen to this challenge with a first of its kind solution. By placing developers needs at the forefront Sei is creating the first parallelized EVM. Embracing EVM:For the first new execution environment to be integrated Sei Labs proposes to support the Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) recognizing its widespread adoption. This strategic proposal acknowledges EVMs current dominance creating a familiar yet enhanced environment for the majority of blockchain developers tools and libraries.Enhancing Ethereum and Eth L2 Applications with Sei:It is often stated that “any large successful application on ETH requiring high throughput will pivot to being their own L2 or their own appchain”. Unfortunately L2s are bandwidth bound by the Ethereum base layer and fundamentally cannot scale while often simultaneously suffering from centralization trade-offs. At the same time appchains incur far more infrastructure overhead risk and complexity than many teams are willing to take on.Sei v2 will bolster any execution environment built atop it with its advanced twin turbo consensus mechanism and parallelization capabilities. This approach equips Ethereum applications to harness Seis speed efficiency and security. What does this mean?This proposed upgrade means that any EVM application can be enhanced with the benefit of 28300 batched transactions per second of throughput with 390 ms time to finality. This allows applications to support many more users and far more ‘web-2’ like interactive experiences than on existing EVM blockchains. As a technology Sei offers far cheaper per-transaction costs higher throughput and the fastest time to finality in crypto while suffering from none of the centralization tradeoffs complexity or the overhead of operating an Ethereum L2 rollup.In this way Sei is making the EVM simple again.Some examples of applications that would benefit from this approach are scalable high performance dexes of any kind massive multiplayer games global payment and settlement applications and NFT projects looking to service mass global audiences. In short: applications that aspire to achieve mass adoption.Wen?Once audits are complete this upgrade will be released in a public testnet in Q1 2024 and will be deployed to mainnet in H1 2024 subject to governance.There are many other important improvements being made to Sei as part of Sei v2; you can read more here: blog.sei.io/sei-v2-the-first…🔴⚪️

tweet_raw: SEC APPEARS HESITANT ON APPROVING THE ETHEREUM ETF- The prospects of a spot #Ethereum exchange-traded fund (ETF) gaining approval from the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) seem dim as indicated by insights from TD Cowen and FOX Business.- Despite recent green lights for #Bitcoin ETFs the SECs stance on Ethereum #ETFs remains cautious.What We Know:TD Cowens Expectations:- TD Cowens Washington Research Group suggests the #SEC is unlikely to approve spot Ethereum ETFs soon.- The bank believes the SEC will seek experience from Bitcoin ETFs before venturing into approvals for other crypto tokens extending the waiting period possibly beyond the 2024 U.S. presidential elections.FOX Business Insights:- FOX Business reporter Eleanor Terrett reveals insider information stating that there is internal resistance at the SEC against approving a spot Ethereum ETF.- The sentiment within the SEC is reported to be a hard no adding an element of uncertainty to the approval process.Commissioner Hester Peirces Perspective:- SEC Commissioner Hester Peirce known for her pro-cryptocurrency stance criticizes the SECs reliance on legal victories for ETF approvals.- She advocates for a more straightforward decision process without court cases compelling action.Asset Managers Optimism:- Despite the reported resistance asset managers behind the ETF applications express confidence.- Reportedly one issuer anticipates approval and a smooth launch based on the success of Bitcoin ETFs.- Another unnamed issuer expects a spot Ethereum ETF by the end of the summer citing positive factors such as earlier approval of Ethereum futures ETFs and strong support from BlackRock.Differing Public Expectations:- Public expectations vary with Bloomberg ETF analyst Eric Balchunas suggesting a 70% chance of approval in May.- JP Morgans Nikolaos Panigirtzoglou predicts a 50% chance while Polymarket odds stand at 53%.- JPMorgan highlights the challenge for the SEC to classify Ethereum as a commodity similar to Bitcoin rather than a security.- Firms like BlackRock and Fidelity despite filing for spot Ethereum ETFs recognize the uncertainties in the regulatory landscape.Image: Bankless#SEC #EthereumETF #Cryptocurrency #BitcoinETF

tweet_raw: I want to give you a little bit of information that will surprise no shock you. In several Middle Eastern countries where they have huge amounts of foreign workers (Kuwait 4.50 million Saudi 13.40 million) they do the following. When a foreign worker arrives the government bank issues the new arrival with a bank account bank ID and credit card. All other banks are forbidden to offer these to foreign workers. Unbeknown to the new worker every month the bank sends a copy of the bank statement of that worker to his/her employer with an exception report of transactions that are unusual. You know any unusual deposits or expenditure. They use this information to detect illegal activity like stealing prostitution and selling drugs etc. This is used extensively many detected monthly jailed or deported. Get this: you know digital ID cashless society???There are private talks in Canberra of introducing a similar system here in Australia. Get it?

tweet_raw: How did we create the most valuable NFT collection on @Polkadot ecosystem as @Neurolanche?🪐Actually technical first NFT of Polkadot? The story of the worlds first WASM NFT on @AstarNetwork;⛓️$50 to $3471 floor price generating a monthly passive income of $140 in $ASTR! 🖼️Step 1.0 ~ StoryAs the team at Neurolanche X Labs we rolled up our sleeves to create a revolution in the health and education sectors while embarking on the steps of a multi-billion dollar project in 2020. We wanted to progress every moment with analytics and scientific advancements. Having big goals in Artificial Intelligence and the Metaverse was not a simple approach. To be honest those who wonder how Neurolanche has achieved such success today do not know that there is a giant team of 23 people behind us.After lengthy academic studies we saw that NFTs were not just a visual element but one of the strongest factors sociologically in building a community. We decided that creating an NFT collection was the right decision to manage the spirit of decentralization in the 7 projects we wanted to create and build a community to support our strong vision. We used first time @ink_lang to create one collection for Neurolauncher!Neurolauncher was always designed to increase in price. Step 2.0 ~ Determining UtilitiesAt the beginning of my writing I mentioned our desire to create a revolution in the health and education sectors. If you wonder to what level Firolauss and Neuroverse will reach you can contact us from our Discord group. Todays topic is Neurolauncher!If you ask me what one of the biggest problems of the Polkadot ecosystem is I could say the absence of an NFT culture and GameFi culture. One of the biggest problems here is the lack of funding and motivation in the projects established. After publishing the Neurolauncher NFT collection we wanted the owners of this NFT collection to have the strongest utilities.By launching the Astar Strike game we created the first Unity-based game in our ecosystem and created a use case for Neurolauncher NFT collections. In addition by allowing other NFT collections within Polkadot to access the Astar Strike game we created significant added value to our community. Moreover we created a passive income mechanism by distributing 30% of our monthly revenue from our $26 million dApp staking program to NFT holders.Step 3.0 Whats Next?As you know we will soon release the Nerox token and build 7 different projects on one token. We understand the importance of decentralization here. In this process by leaving the treasury management to the NFT owners we want our community to be managed in a decentralized manner. As the CEO of Neurolanche I hold 1 NFT to not influence the process. In addition we will AirDrop 5% of Nerox tokens supply to Neurolauncher NFT owners.Step 4.0 Final WordWe will never forget those who have supported us so far. Our promise to you as the Neurolanche team is to continue working without losing our motivation. Everything will be different when we enter under the roof of a company worth $500 million this week. Trust the plan!To become a Neurolauncher NFT owner and join this adventure you can reach the @ParasHQ NFT marketplace through the link below.Nft Marketplace: astar.paras.id/collection/bY……LeoCEO Neurolanche X Labs

tweet_raw: 🐳 NFT研报 – Clashub该线程为@theclashub的介绍，主要涵盖了 Clashub 的背景、特点、在业界的成就及其未来计划进行分析。🧵ʕ•̫͡•ʕ•̫͡•  以下为Clashub相关介绍  ʕ•̫͡•ʕ•̫͡•✦ 项目介绍Clashub 是一个基于 NFT 的卡牌游戏平台，可以为所有发布的 NFT 系列实现 Play to Earn。Clashub 算法将玩家拥有的 NFT 转换为可玩的游戏卡片，允许他们使用这些 NFT 卡片与真实对手对战，并有机会赢得 $CLASH 代币。✰ 项目亮点Clashub 最显著的特点是它提供了一个游戏平台，不同网络和收藏系列的 NFT 可以在同一游戏板上使用。在 Clashub 中，用户可以找到数十种不同的 Power-UPs 来制定策略，Mint Tickets 用于获取特殊收藏系列的 #NFT，以及特殊的 Tournament Pass 参加比赛。Clashub 在 2023 年迪拜的 AIBC 欧亚大会的 #GameFi  类别中获得了第一名，该奖项是在测试阶段获得的，可见Clashub 的潜力很大。✰ VIP PASS NFT铸造细节-总供应量: 999 -铸造价格: #FreeMint-铸造网络: #ETH-铸造日期：TBA-权益：2024/Q1可获得 $Clash 代币空投ʕ•̫͡•ʔ•̫͡•  如果喜欢，请一键三连 !  ʕ•̫͡•ʕ•̫͡•
